              <span id="reviewTextContainer2982570342" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15751480447079593003">A good story from the WWII period of Germany. The story speaks to the horrors of this time and how a few German citizens did their part to thwart the NAZIs. The characters were very good and worked well together. The story is also entertaining. I really enjoyed the book. I read the second book first and I recommend reading them in order.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


