              <span id="reviewTextContainer783918077" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7397162908287298501">I received this from Goodreads First Reads program.<br/><br/>I thought that this novel was an incredibly powerful novel about WWII. Not many books discuss the treatment of handicapped individuals at the hands of Nazi Germany. This novel is well written and pretty accurate. I think this is a great novel for young adults because so few young adult novels accurately portray the atrocities committed by Nazis. I think the character of Sophie will stick with me for a long time. This is the best young adult nove</span>
  <span id="freeText7397162908287298501" style="display:none">I received this from Goodreads First Reads program.<br /><br />I thought that this novel was an incredibly powerful novel about WWII. Not many books discuss the treatment of handicapped individuals at the hands of Nazi Germany. This novel is well written and pretty accurate. I think this is a great novel for young adults because so few young adult novels accurately portray the atrocities committed by Nazis. I think the character of Sophie will stick with me for a long time. This is the best young adult novel I have read in a long time and I can't wait until my nieces and nephews are old enough to read it.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7397162908287298501" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

