              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer700423734086714886">I loved this book. I really liked the character, Sophie Adler and the choices she made. I thought it was an interesting story and how children of that time were recruited into the Hitler youth. A wonderful story of a hero who makes a significant difference in the lives of many. </span>

          </span>
